# ============================================
#
# EmailSignin Error Solutions:
# 1. Verify EMAIL_SERVER URL format (not separate variables)
# 2. Test SMTP credentials independently
# 3. Check NEXTAUTH_URL matches your domain
# 4. Ensure NEXTAUTH_SECRET is 32+ characters
# 5. Verify email provider allows SMTP connections
